pan><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"89412\" style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;\" data-color=\"#9bc3b7\"><section><section data-width=\"40px\" style=\"width: 40px;height: 40px;border-width: 2px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(155, 195, 183);border-radius: 50%;margin-left: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);text-align: center;padding: 3px;transform: rotateZ(0deg);\"><section data-width=\"30px\" style=\"width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;color: #ffffff;text-align: center;line-height: 30px;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;background-color: #9bc3b7;transform: rotate(0deg);\"><span class=\"\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">3</span></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"border-top: 2px solid #9bc3b7;margin-top: -18px;padding: 23px 15px 15px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;background-color: #f5f5f5;\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">另外，这一款英飞凌与安普盛联手打造的智能马桶盖方案，为终端厂商提供的不仅是一套成熟、稳定的整体解决思路，还包括了整个过程的售前、售后、技术工程人员等</span><strong style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(171, 55, 122);\">服务支持</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">，助力打造更具优势的智能产品！</span></p></section></section></section><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">拥有众多创新的技术与商业优势，这款智能马桶盖方案决心将<strong>“懂你”</strong>进行到底，全力搞定<strong>消费者与终端厂商</strong>的多</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">重需求！随着这么优质的方案在国内推广，大家也不用再远赴东洋买马桶盖了，是不是很赞？<img data-src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/mpres/htmledition/images/icon/common/emotion_panel/emoji_wx/2_06.png\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"20\" style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: text-bottom; width: 20px !important; height: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;\" _width=\"20px\" src=\"https://